*** Test Cases ***
Launch browser
    Open Browser    https://www.tutorialspoint.com/selenium/practice/selenium_automation_practice.php    ${BROWSER}
    Maximize Browser Window
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    xpath://input[@id='name']    10s

Input First Name
    Input Text    xpath://input[@id='name']    Manoj
    Sleep    3s

Input Last Name
    Input Text    xpath://input[@id='email']    manoj@gmail.com
    Sleep    3s

Select Gender
    Click Element    xpath://label[normalize-space()='Male']
    Sleep    3s

Select mobile
    Input Text    xpath://input[@id='mobile']       1234567890
    Sleep    3s

Input Date
    Input Text    xpath://input[@id='dob']    15/01/2026
    Sleep    3s
Input subject
    Input Text    xpath://input[@id='subjects']    hello
Select hobbies
    Click Element    xpath://label[normalize-space()='Sports']
    Sleep    3s

Upload File
    Choose File    xpath://input[@id='picture']   ${FILE_PATH}
    Sleep    3s

select address
    Input Text    xpath://textarea[@id='picture']    hyd
select state
    Select From List By Value    xpath://select[@id='state']    NCR
    Select From List By Label    xpath://select[@id='city']     Agra

Submit Form
    Click Button    xpath://input[@value='Login']
    Sleep    3s
    Close Browser
